Value MAC (\S+)
Value IP (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value USERNAME (\S+)
Value DEVICE_TYPE (\S+)
Value DEVICE_NAME (\S+)

Start
  ^Client MAC Address : ${MAC}
  ^Client IPv4 Address : ${IP}
  ^Client Username : ${USERNAME}
  ^\s+Device Type\s+: ${DEVICE_TYPE}
  ^\s+Device Name\s+: ${DEVICE_NAME} -> Record
